title: memzbuck
author: memzbuck
content: As title says. Making you aware that Bitcoin Core 25.0 is officially out, even the binaries are out. Links will be provided.Github: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/releases/tag/v25.0Bitcoin Core binaries: https://bitcoincore.org/bin/bitcoin-core-25.0/Also, be sure to verify your binary with GPG. Don't Trust but Verify. Feel free to read documentation for low level changes.
